text: Lunner is a municipality in Akershus county, Norway. In 2022, 9,144 people lived there. It is part of the traditional district Hadeland.https://snl.no/Lunner. SNL.no History: It was part of Oppland county until 2020. It was part of Viken county, from 1 January 2020. == Related pages == * List of mayors in Norway that are elected until 2027 ==References== Category:Municipalities of Akershus
